f=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615639\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615639\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 03, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rjw1665702578992.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rjw1665702578992.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rjw1665702578992.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rjw1665702578992\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__end_216944\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Marks the end of a ProcScript module, operation, or trigger.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__topic_d71444e1_d71445e1_d71446e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__p_d71447e1_d71448e1_d71449e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">end</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__topic_d46977e1_d46978e1_d46979e1_d46980e1_d46981e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d411823e65\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__p_d71453e1_d71454e1_d71455e1\">None. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">end</span> statement does not affect the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__topic_d46982e1_d46983e1_d46984e1_d46985e1_d46986e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d411823e80\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__d6049e20\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__topic_d46987e1_d46988e1_d46989e1_d46990e1_d46991e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d411823e89\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__p_d71465e1_d71466e1_d71467e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">end</span> statement indicates the end\n            of a ProcScript module or operation. If this statement is encountered during execution,\n            an implicit <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">done</span> is executed and the module or operation ends,\n            returning the current value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>. If an\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">function</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">operation</span> statement or the end of\n            the trigger is encountered, an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">end</span> (and implicit\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">done</span>) for the previous ProcScript module or operation is\n            assumed.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__p_d71468e1_d71469e1_d71470e1\">ProcScript statements after an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">end</span>\n            are not recognized unless they are part of another ProcScript module or operation. That\n            is, if ProcScript statements following an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">end</span> are meant to be\n            executed, the statement immediately following the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">end</span> should be a\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">function</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">operation</span> statement.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__p_d71471e1_d71472e1_d71473e1\">Labels defined with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">blockdata</span> statements must be defined at the end of a ProcScript module or operation, before the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">end</span> statement is encountered.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows the use of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">end</span> for a\n               trigger and a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">function</span> statement:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger store \ncall LSTORE\nend ; end store\n\n; container: Local ProcScript Modules (component-level)\nfunction LSTORE\n store\n if ($status &lt; 0)\n message \"Store error!\"\n rollback\n else\n message \"Store done.\"\n commit\n endif\nend ; end LSTORE function\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__section_uxr_xdc_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d411823e163\">Example: Defining an Operation</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows the operation <code class=\"ph codeph\">DISCOUNT</code> of a\n            service component named SERV1:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__pre_gn1_ydc_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation DISCOUNT\nparams\n  string CUSTID : IN\n  numeric AMOUNT : INOUT\n  numeric PERCENTAGE : OUT\nendparams\n; no discount till proven otherwise\n; 20% discount for Uniface\n; 15% discount for Acme\n; adjust amount\nPERCENTAGE = 0\nif ( CUSTID == \"ufbv\" ) PERCENTAGE = 20\nif ( CUSTID == \"acme\" ) PERCENTAGE = 15\nAMOUNT = AMOUNT * ( 100 - PERCENTAGE) / 100\nend\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The operation <code class=\"ph codeph\">DISCOUNT</code> could be referenced from another\n            component as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rjw1665702578992__pre_hn1_ydc_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">activate \"SERV1\".DISCOUNT (ID.CUST, TOTAL.INVOICE, $DISCOUNT$)\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aqg1665702579072.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>entry</a><p>Declare a ProcScript entry, a script module that can be invoked from within the same component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pub1707739948228.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>operation</a><p>Declare an operation ProcScript module.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tdk1676354384534.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>function...end</a><p>Declare a ProcScript function, a script module that can be invoked from other modules in its vicinity.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615639\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615639\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "end Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 03, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Marks the end of a ProcScript module, operation, or trigger. end Return Values None. The end statement does not affect the value of $status . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The end statement indicates the end of a ProcScript module or operation. If this statement is encountered during execution, an implicit done is executed and the module or operation ends, returning the current value of $status . If an function or operation statement or the end of the trigger is encountered, an end (and implicit done ) for the previous ProcScript module or operation is assumed. ProcScript statements after an end are not recognized unless they are part of another ProcScript module or operation. That is, if ProcScript statements following an end are meant to be executed, the statement immediately following the end should be a function or operation statement. Labels defined with blockdata statements must be defined at the end of a ProcScript module or operation, before the end statement is encountered. The following example shows the use of end for a trigger and a function statement: trigger store call LSTORE end ; end store ; container: Local ProcScript Modules (component-level) function LSTORE store if ($status < 0) message \"Store error!\" rollback else message \"Store done.\" commit endif end ; end LSTORE function Copy Example: Defining an Operation The following example shows the operation DISCOUNT of a service component named SERV1: operation DISCOUNT params string CUSTID : IN numeric AMOUNT : INOUT numeric PERCENTAGE : OUT endparams ; no discount till proven otherwise ; 20% discount for Uniface ; 15% discount for Acme ; adjust amount PERCENTAGE = 0 if ( CUSTID == \"ufbv\" ) PERCENTAGE = 20 if ( CUSTID == \"acme\" ) PERCENTAGE = 15 AMOUNT = AMOUNT * ( 100 - PERCENTAGE) / 100 end Copy The operation DISCOUNT could be referenced from another component as follows: activate \"SERV1\".DISCOUNT (ID.CUST, TOTAL.INVOICE, $DISCOUNT$) Copy Related Links entry Declare a ProcScript entry, a script module that can be invoked from within the same component. operation Declare an operation ProcScript module. function...end Declare a ProcScript function, a script module that can be invoked from other modules in its vicinity. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}